{"tid":2356284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北韓第八次代表大會舉行　金正恩稱要振興國家經濟","createTime":"2021-01-06T16:47:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T16:55:25.000Z","uid":90457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"17db7b4b79f45f71556ca96f2e22fe537a01cabd","tid":2356284,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T16:47:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1568874-20210106.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1568874-20210106.htm&d=tgCcTb3Ji4LFIEkqsM1g5lNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=63a0b61e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1568874-20210106.htm&h=5ea46b3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1568874-20210106.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n北韓勞動黨第八次代表大會昨日舉行，官方朝中社報道，領袖金正恩在會上表示，要按照新的五年計劃，開展進一步振興國家經濟的工作。<br />\n<br />\n報道說，金正恩分析了國家經濟發展五年戰略中，出現的缺點及主客觀因素，並總結過去取得的成果。他又提出爭取社會主義建設劃時代進展、推動統一事業和對外關係，以及加強黨發展工作的一系列問題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beedaff22bc6c1ed67c4cc35e811278a1df1d216","tid":2356284,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T16:48:54.000Z","msg":"北伐搶支那最快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9751725cc71e411edc45b8a1a6363218e33d4ed4","tid":2356284,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"beedaff22bc6c1ed67c4cc35e811278a1df1d216","tid":2356284,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T16:48:54.000Z","msg":"北伐搶支那最快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01